sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_script"><sys_transform_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><map display_value="Africa Hardware Asset">f8a5d0118740e5545b9aa9383cbb3535</map><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[function runTransformScript(source, map, log, target) {
    // Extract serial number from source
    var serialNumber = source.u_serial_number;

    // Check if the serial number already exists in the target table
    var gr = new GlideRecord('alm_hardware');
    gr.addQuery('serial_number', serialNumber);
    gr.query();

    // If the serial number exists, set ignore to true
    if (gr.next()) {
        if (action == "update") {
            gs.log('Ignoring record because the serial number already exists in the target table: ' + serialNumber);
            ignore = true;
            return;
        }
    } else {
        gs.log('Processing record for serial number: ' + serialNumber);
        ignore = false;
    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_transform_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>a-maseem</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-11-13 19:34:07</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>3229402283795650c2323d426daad3b1</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onBefore</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions" source="x_dgs_int_global">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_script_3229402283795650c2323d426daad3b1</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>a-abhchavandttl</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-11-28 11:40:43</sys_updated_on><when>onBefore</when></sys_transform_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_567a6f6e87f795905b9aa9383cbb3532
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>GET</http_method><name>GETDetails</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process( /*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
    // implement resource here
    var cnt = 0;
    var resultsArr = [];
    var cmp_code = [];
    var getQuery = request.queryParams.query;
    var getLimit = request.queryParams.top;
    var start = parseInt(request.queryParams.start) || 0; // default set to 10
    var pagesize = parseInt(request.queryParams.top) || 500; // default set to 500
    var end = start + pagesize; // new line
    var rowcount = start;   // new line
    var qr = 'u_member_firm=c076ad120feac300dc2fc7dce1050e5b';
    if(getQuery){
        qr = qr + '^'+getQuery;
    }
    var ga = new GlideAggregate('alm_hardware');
    ga.groupBy('company');
    ga.addEncodedQuery(getQuery);
    ga.query();
    while (ga.next()) {
        // check if the row is for a unique value and not for an overall count
        if (ga.getDisplayValue('company')) {
            cmp_code[ga.getDisplayValue('company')] = ga.company.u_company_id; // add the value to the array
        }
    }
    var grasset = new GlideRecord('alm_hardware');
    grasset.addEncodedQuery(qr);
    grasset.chooseWindow(start,end);
	grasset.orderByDesc('sys_updated_on');
   // if(getLimit){
      //  grasset.setLimit(getLimit);
    //}
    grasset.query();
    var totalRows = grasset.getRowCount();
    countRecord = grasset.getRowCount();
    while (grasset.next()) {
        //cnt++;
        var result = {};
        result.index = rowcount;
        result.model = grasset.getDisplayValue('model');
        result.serial_number = grasset.getDisplayValue('serial_number');
        result.model_category = grasset.getDisplayValue('model_category');
        result.asset_tag = grasset.getDisplayValue('asset_tag');
                if (grasset.install_status == '6') {
                    result.stockroom = grasset.getDisplayValue('stockroom');
                    result.stockroom_code = grasset.stockroom.u_stockroom_code;
                }
        result.employee_code = grasset.assigned_to.u_local_employee_number;  
        result.sys_class_name = grasset.getDisplayValue('sys_class_name');
        result.company_name = grasset.getDisplayValue('company');
        result.company_code = cmp_code[grasset.getDisplayValue('company')];
        //         if (grasset.company != '' && cmp_code[grasset.company] == undefined) {
        //             cmp_code[grasset.company] = grasset.company.u_company_id;
        //         }
        // result.capmpany_code =cmp_code[grasset.company];
        result.install_date = grasset.install_date;
        result.retirement_date = grasset.retirement_date;
        resultsArr.push(result);
        ++rowcount;
    }
    var nextPageStart = (end>totalRows)? null:rowcount;
    var responseBody2 = {};
    responseBody2.status = "Successfully Retrived: " + pagesize + " assets" + start + "start "+ end + "end" + rowcount + "rowcount" + nextPageStart + "nextpagestart";
    responseBody2.details = resultsArr;
    response.setBody(responseBody2);
    var gr_logs = new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_api_transaction_error_log_global');
    gr_logs.initialize();
    gr_logs.api_uri = 'GET /api/x_dgs_int_global/africasapassetintrgration';
    gr_logs.request = 'Get asset for Africa member firm';
    //gr_logs.u_request_body=requestBody;

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>Post asset</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process( /*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {


    var requestBody = request.body.dataString;
    var parsedData = JSON.parse(requestBody);

    var countP = 0,countI=0,countU=0;
    var countF = 0;
    var failedRowsArray = [];
    var insertedrec = '';
    var responsearr = [];

    var imp = new dttl_CreatImportsetasync();
    var isId = imp.createImportSet("x_dgs_int_global_africa_asset_staging", "Africa Hardware Asset");
    for (var i = 0; i < parsedData.length; i++) {


        var gr = new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_africa_asset_staging');
        gr.initialize();
        gr.sys_import_set = isId.sys_id;
        gr.u_model = parsedData[i].model;
        gr.u_serial_number = parsedData[i].serial_number;
        gr.u_asset_tag = parsedData[i].asset_tag;
        gr.u_model_category = parsedData[i].model_category;
        gr.u_assigned_to = parsedData[i].assigned_to;
        gr.u_company = parsedData[i].company;
        if(parsedData[i].stockroom_code){
			gr.u_stockroom = parsedData[i].stockroom_code;
		}else{
			gr.u_stockroom = parsedData[i].stockroom;
		}
        gr.u_installed = parsedData[i].install_date;
        gr.u_retired_date = parsedData[i].retired;
        gr.insert();
    }
    imp.setStateTransform(isId);

    var grN = new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_africa_asset_staging');
    grN.orderByDesc('sys_created_on');
    grN.setLimit(parsedData.length);
    grN.addQuery('sys_import_set=' + gr.sys_import_set);
    grN.query();
    while (grN.next()) {
        if (!grN.sys_row_error && !grN.sys_import_state_comment.toString().includes("Error : ")) {
			if(grN.sys_import_state=='inserted')
				countP++;
			else if(grN.sys_import_state=='ignored')
				countI++;
			else if(grN.sys_import_state=='updated')
				countU++;
            var responseBodyP = {};
            responseBodyP.Status = "Record "+grN.sys_import_state;
            responseBodyP.serial_number = grN.u_serial_number.getDisplayValue();
            responsearr.push(responseBodyP);
        } else {
            countF++;
            var responseBodyF = {};
            responseBodyF.Status = "Record Failed to Transform";
           responseBodyF.serial_number = grN.u_serial_number.getDisplayValue();
            if (grN.sys_row_error.error_message)
                responseBodyF.error_message = grN.sys_row_error.error_message;
            else
                responseBodyF.error_message = grN.sys_import_state_comment;
            //Push only failed ROW numbers into failedRowsArray
            failedRowsArray.push(grN.sys_import_row.getDisplayValue());

            responsearr.push(responseBodyF);
        }
    }

    var responseBody2 = {};
    responseBody2.status = "Successfully Inserted: " + countP + " , Updated " + countU + " Ignored "+ countI +" and Failed: " + countF;
    responseBody2.details = responsearr;
    response.setBody(responseBody2);
	
	var gr_logs=new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_api_transaction_error_log_global');
	gr_logs.initialize();
	gr_logs.api_uri = 'POST /api/x_dgs_int_global/africasapassetintrgration/asset';
	gr_logs.request ='Update or create asset for Africa member firm';
	gr_logs.u_request_body=requestBody;
	gr_logs.u_response=responseBody2;
	gr_logs.insert();

    // implement resource here

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_dgs_int_global/africasapassetintrgration/asset</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/asset</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><requires_snc_internal_role>true</requires_snc_internal_role><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>a-sunrathod</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-12-27 11:16:34</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>4d1b90dd8780e5545b9aa9383cbb35af</sys_id><sys_mod_count>19</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Post asset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions" source="x_dgs_int_global">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_4d1b90dd8780e5545b9aa9383cbb35af</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>a-sodhal</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-07-25 12:14:26</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="AfricaSAPAssetIntrgration">2f3a236e87f795905b9aa9383cbb35c9</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_dgs_int_global.africaAsset</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>africaAsset</name><script><![CDATA[var africaAsset = Class.create();
africaAsset.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},

    updateLog: function(resultsArr) {
        var grGetLogs = new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_api_transaction_error_log_global');
        grGetLogs.initialize();
        grGetLogs.api_uri = 'GET /api/x_dgs_int_global/africaAssetsapassetintrgration';
        grGetLogs.request = 'Get asset for Africa member firm';
        //grGetLogs.u_request_body=requestBody;
        grGetLogs.u_response = resultsArr;
        grGetLogs.insert();
    },

    updatePostLogs: function(requestBody,responseBody2) {
        var gr_logs = new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_api_transaction_error_log_global');
        gr_logs.initialize();
        gr_logs.api_uri = 'POST /api/x_dgs_int_global/africasapassetintrgration/asset';
        gr_logs.request = 'Update or create asset for Africa member firm';
        gr_logs.u_request_body = requestBody;
        gr_logs.u_response = responseBody2;
        gr_logs.insert();
    },

	createImportSet: function(sys_id,parsedData){
		
        var gr = new GlideRecord('x_dgs_int_global_africa_asset_staging');
        gr.initialize();
        gr.sys_import_set = sys_id;
        gr.u_model = parsedData.model;
        gr.u_serial_number = parsedData.serial_number;
        gr.u_asset_tag = parsedData.asset_tag;
        gr.u_model_category = parsedData.model_category;
        gr.u_assigned_to = parsedData.assigned_to;
        gr.u_company = parsedData.company;
		if(parsedData.stockroom_code){
			gr.u_stockroom = parsedData.stockroom_code;
		}else{
			gr.u_stockroom = parsedData.stockroom;
		}
        //gr.u_stockroom = parsedData.stockroom;
        gr.u_installed = parsedData.install_date;
        gr.u_retired_date = parsedData.retired;
        gr.insert();
	},


    type: 'africaAsset'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>a-aranithadttl</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-07-24 13:21:58</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>34c04a1a83238ad0c2323d426daad38d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>10</sys_mod_count><sys_name>africaAsset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions" source="x_dgs_int_global">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_34c04a1a83238ad0c2323d426daad38d</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>a-aranithadttl</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-07-25 10:17:59</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_script"><sys_transform_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><map/><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[function runTransformScript(source, map, log, target) {
    // Extract serial number from source
    var serialNumber = source.u_serial_number;

    // Check if the serial number already exists in the target table
    var gr = new GlideRecord('alm_hardware');
    gr.addQuery('serial_number', u_serial_number);
    gr.query();

    // If the serial number exists, set ignore to true
    if (gr.next()) {
        log.info('Ignoring record because the serial number already exists in the target table: ' + serialNumber);
        ignore = true;
    } else {
        log.info('Processing record for serial number: ' + serialNumber);
        ignore = false;
    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_transform_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>a-maseem</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-11-13 19:25:46</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>3a56482283795650c2323d426daad393</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onBefore</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions" source="x_dgs_int_global">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Integration_CoE_Global_Functions">fcd39f69874dd514162020ee8bbb353e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_script_3a56482283795650c2323d426daad393</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>a-maseem</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-11-13 19:35:24</sys_updated_on><when>onBefore</when></sys_transform_script></record_update>
